# <%= @current_collective.private_workspace? ? "Workspace" : "Collective" %> Settings

<%= render 'shared/collective_tier_badge', collective: @current_collective %>

<% if @current_collective.archived? && @current_tenant.feature_enabled?("stripe_billing") %>
<% if @current_collective.created_by_id && @current_user.id == @current_collective.created_by_id %>
**Status: Inactive** — This collective is deactivated and not being billed. [Manage on billing page](/billing)
<% else %>
**Status: Inactive** — This collective is deactivated and not being billed. Only the collective creator can reactivate it.
<% end %>

<% else %>
Current settings for **<%= @current_collective.name %>**:

| Setting | Value |
|---------|-------|
| Name | <%= @current_collective.name %> |
| Handle | <%= @current_collective.handle %> |
| Description | <%= @current_collective.description || "(none)" %> |
| Timezone | <%= @current_collective.timezone %> |
| Tempo | <%= @current_collective.tempo %> |
| Synchronization Mode | <%= @current_collective.synchronization_mode %> |
<% unless @current_collective.private_workspace? %>
| Invitations | <%= @current_collective.all_members_can_invite? ? 'All members can invite' : 'Only admins can invite' %> |
| Representation | <%= @current_collective.any_member_can_represent? ? 'Any member can represent' : 'Only representatives' %> |
<% end %>
<%
  available_flags = FeatureFlagService.all_flags.select { |f|
    FeatureFlagService.tenant_enabled?(@current_tenant, f) &&
      FeatureFlagService.flag_metadata(f).fetch("collective_level", false)
  }
  tier_in_effect = @current_tenant.feature_enabled?("stripe_billing")
  if tier_in_effect
    paid_flags, free_flags = available_flags.partition { |f| Collective::PAID_FEATURE_FLAGS.include?(f) }
  else
    paid_flags, free_flags = [], available_flags
  end
%>
<% if free_flags.any? %>

## <%= tier_in_effect ? "Features" : "Features Enabled" %>

| Feature | Enabled |
|---------|---------|
<% free_flags.each do |flag_name| %>
<% metadata = FeatureFlagService.flag_metadata(flag_name) %>
| <%= metadata['name'] %> | <%= @current_collective.feature_flag_enabled_locally?(flag_name) ? 'Yes' : 'No' %> |
<% end %>
<% end %>
<% if tier_in_effect && !@current_collective.is_main_collective? %>

## Paid Plan Features

<% if @current_collective.paid_tier? %>
This collective is on the paid plan ($3/month).

| Feature | Enabled |
|---------|---------|
| Automations | <%= @current_collective.automation_rules.enabled.count %> enabled — [Manage](<%= @current_collective.path %>/settings/automations) |
<% paid_flags.each do |flag_name| %>
<% metadata = FeatureFlagService.flag_metadata(flag_name) %>
| <%= metadata['name'] %> | <%= @current_collective.feature_flag_enabled_locally?(flag_name) ? 'Yes' : 'No' %> |
<% end %>

To move this collective back to the free plan, POST to `<%= @current_collective.path %>/downgrade`. Enabled automations will be disabled and Trio / file attachments will be turned off.
<% elsif @current_collective.requires_stripe_billing? %>
**Billing lapsed** — paid features are paused. Restore your subscription at [/billing](/billing) to resume.
<% else %>
Upgrade to the paid plan ($3/month) to unlock Automations, Trio AI assistant, and file attachments on this collective. POST to `<%= @current_collective.path %>/upgrade` (owner only).
<% end %>
<% end %>
<% if @current_collective.feature_enabled?('api') && !@current_collective.private_workspace? && @collective_ai_agents.present? %>

## AI Agents in this Collective

<% @collective_ai_agents.each do |ai_agent| %>
* [<%= ai_agent.display_name %>](<%= ai_agent.path %>) - managed by <%= ai_agent.parent ? "[#{ai_agent.parent.display_name}](#{ai_agent.parent.path})" : "Unknown" %>
<% end %>
<% end %>

<% if @current_tenant.feature_enabled?("stripe_billing") && !@current_collective.is_main_collective? && @current_collective.paid_tier? %>
<% if @current_collective.billing_exempt? %>
Billing-exempt by an admin. [View billing](/billing)
<% else %>
[Manage billing](/billing)
<% end %>
<% end %>

<% unless tier_in_effect && !@current_collective.is_main_collective? %>

## Additional Settings

* [Manage Automations](<%= @current_collective.path %>/settings/automations) - Configure event-triggered actions, webhooks, and schedules
<% end %>
<% end %>
